---
import Fallback from "../../assets/blog-placeholder-about.jpg";
---

<!-- Contenedor principal -->
<div
  class="mx-auto mt-20 flex max-w-6xl flex-col items-center gap-8 px-6 lg:flex-row "
>
  <!-- Imagen -->
  <div
    class="border-primary h-64 w-64 overflow-hidden rounded-2xl shadow-lg md:h-96 md:w-96 drop-shadow-[4px_4px_0_#7836cf]"
  >
    <img
      src={Fallback.src}
      alt="个人头像占位图"
      class="h-full w-full object-cover"
      width="800"
      height="800"
      loading="lazy"
      decoding="async"
    />
  </div>

  <!-- Texto -->
  <div class="flex-1 text-center text-gray-300 lg:text-left">
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white">关于我</h2>
    <p class="mt-4 text-gray-200 leading-relaxed">
      教育背景：中南大学 能源与动力工程 本科（辅修工商管理）。当前专注于 AI 应用工程化（RAG/Agent）、云原生与存储以及量化系统工程。技术栈覆盖 Python/Go/TypeScript、FastAPI/Flask、LangChain/RAGFlow、Kubernetes/CSI、Elasticsearch/Milvus 等。
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
